"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.17\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.17</span> 標題：旗、旌旗（standard, ensign, banner）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אוֹת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’oth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:2\">NUM 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:4\">PSA 74:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:4\">PSA 74:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： דגל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： dagal（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:6\">PSA 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:4\">SNG 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:10\">SNG 6:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： דֶּגֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： degel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:52\">NUM 1:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:2\">NUM 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:3\">NUM 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:10\">NUM 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:17\">NUM 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:18\">NUM 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:25\">NUM 2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:31\">NUM 2:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num2:34\">NUM 2:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:14\">NUM 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:18\">NUM 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:22\">NUM 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:25\">NUM 10:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:4\">SNG 2:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： נֵס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： nes)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:15\">EXO 17:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:8\">NUM 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:9\">NUM 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:6\">PSA 60:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:26\">ISA 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:10\">ISA 11:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:12\">ISA 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:2\">ISA 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:3\">ISA 18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:17\">ISA 30:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:9\">ISA 31:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:22\">ISA 49:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:10\">ISA 62:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:6\">JER 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:21\">JER 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:2\">JER 50:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:12\">JER 51:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:27\">JER 51:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:7\">EZK 27:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： נסס</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： nasas（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:16\">ZEC 9:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： תֹּרֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： toren)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:17\">ISA 30:17</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0394_standards.png\" alt=\"不同式樣的參旗\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">不同式樣的參旗 (Cyclopedia of Biblical, Theological and Ecclesiastical Literature, Harper 1888, Public domain)</figcaption></figure>旌旗是一個特別顯眼的標誌，用來識別一個特定的群體。它可以是固定在一根長杆上面的旗幟或板。在很多情況下，這是一個固定在杆子末端的金屬物件或圖像（例如鷹或獅子的頭），固定方式很像在槍桿上固定槍頭。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0395_standards_hant.jpg\" alt=\"參旗\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">參旗 (© Original file by Steerpike (File:Arch of Titus Menorah.png), CC BY 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>上列的希伯來文詞語同時出現在軍事和宗教語境中。在作戰時，旌旗會被軍隊帶上戰場，並作為士兵的集合點。如果戰鬥獲勝或者奪取了一個重要的據點，勝利方就會在那裡豎立旌旗，表示獲得了勝利。如果某種語言並不熟悉旗幟或旌旗，翻譯者可以用以下方式表達<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:4\">PSA 74:4</a> ：「他們已經把獲勝的標記放在這裡」，或「他們已經豎起標記，表示他們擊敗了我們」。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:16\">EXO 17:16</a> 有一個文本上的問題。希伯來文本作<em>kes</em> ，意思是「座位」或「寶座」，有些譯本接受一個校訂的文本<em>nes</em> ，這個詞語在上一節也出現過；例如，這節經文的前半節可譯作：「他說：『高舉主的旌旗！』」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）。有些譯本保留<em>kes</em> ，不採用校訂文本；例如，「他說：『因手已舉起達到主的寶座』」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 直譯）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:16\">ZEC 9:16</a> ：希伯來文動詞<em>mithnossoth</em> 的準確意思存疑。如果這個詞和<em>nes</em> 有關，那麼直譯是「像旌旗那樣被舉起」。不過，只有幾個譯本（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"King James Version (1611)\">KJV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> 、《武加大譯本》）表達了這種含義。大部分翻譯者和解經家都認為這個詞和另一個希伯來文詞根相關聯，該詞根的意思是「照耀」或「閃耀」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
